    # 3ï¸âƒ£ A variable name can only contain alpha-numeric characters and underscores (A-z, 0-9, and _ )
    # 4ï¸âƒ£ Variable names are case-sensitive
    # 5ï¸âƒ£ Avoid using Python keywords as variable names

